7* basic calculator
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
num1 = input("Enter a number: ")
num2 = input("Enter another number: ")
result = num1 + num2
print(result)  
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
默认得到字符串
转换
|a| int()
result = int(num1) + int(num2)

